00:27.387 --> 00:29.083
He won't stay down for long.

00:30.386 --> 00:31.995
You must find Wil.

00:32.894 --> 00:34.093
He is our last hope.

00:34.100 --> 00:35.266
I'm not leaving without you.

00:38.838 --> 00:41.272
Go now. Find Wil!

00:44.377 --> 00:46.444
Father, you're too weak, he'll kill you!

00:47.747 --> 00:49.681
I must try to end this now.

00:50.317 --> 00:51.349
No!

01:10.170 --> 01:11.202
Don't be afraid.

01:12.105 --> 01:13.905
I will always be with you.

01:14.941 --> 01:15.973
Now go.

01:46.873 --> 01:48.106
- Mareth.
- Wil!

01:48.113 --> 01:49.212
The Warlock Lord is here!

01:49.219 --> 01:51.286
- Allanon saved me, but...
- I have to help.

01:51.293 --> 01:53.393
He can't take him alone. Allanon!

02:05.656 --> 02:06.989
No!

02:07.327 --> 02:08.658
_

02:20.894 --> 02:21.973
No!

02:23.865 --> 02:24.931
Wil!

02:32.352 --> 02:33.518
Allanon!

02:39.426 --> 02:43.127
<i>I feel it running through my veins â™ª</i>

03:16.534 --> 03:19.698
